# Cloudflare Pages headers for the dwc-validator project.
#
# Cache strategy: long-cache only the version-suffixed wheel (its name
# changes on every release, so it's safe to mark immutable). Everything
# else (index.html, app.js, app.css, manifest.json) revalidates often
# so a deployed fix reaches users without manual cache-bust.
#
# Cloudflare Pages applies the LAST matching rule when headers collide,
# so the most-specific rules go at the bottom.

# Default: short cache, revalidate. Index pages, JS, CSS, manifest.
/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=300

# Versioned wheel: immutable, fully cacheable. Filename includes the
# package version (dwc_sidecar-X.Y.Z-py3-none-any.whl) so a new release
# changes the path and the old cached entry is naturally orphaned.
/*.whl
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
